{"tid":2385794,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"你地會點處理D餸汁","createTime":"2021-01-29T08:20:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-30T18:36:36.000Z","uid":103263,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"85d937b6c5b4f9c7d2f0c10fc7281dacfdc30e2d","tid":2385794,"uid":103263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"例如，外賣食完D米線，你地會唔會先倒左D湯，然後先掉左佢<br />\n<br />\n我見同一層樓D鄰居，往往見到佢地真係成盒湯都唔倒就咁包好就掉，如果清潔工人唔夠時間清理，會搞到成層都好大陣味<br />\n<br />\n點解連倒D汁/湯去廁所或者鋅盤都懶呢......"},{"pid":"02b1c0e42b4478d46c6a55fa01d05ac922746991","tid":2385794,"uid":122516,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:20:58.000Z","msg":"飲哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7946cce3708629790f33da1a7b5b94fcbd4e84","tid":2385794,"uid":98473,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:23:21.000Z","msg":"多數會倒落廁所<br />\n如果多廚餘 驚沖唔到廁<br />\n會包多兩三個膠袋先放出走廊"},{"pid":"d791e9b4133468b50797193cd175cbfcd3411b6a","tid":2385794,"uid":84783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"Sink"},{"pid":"e21a6a1ba33dd7efbd17117e31131dd7cbe21259","tid":2385794,"uid":17641,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:25:33.000Z","msg":"淋隔離屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f625d9f8da2e22e8ecaf4ccd6195cd78019775","tid":2385794,"uid":27324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d7946cce3708629790f33da1a7b5b94fcbd4e84","tid":2385794,"uid":98473,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:23:21.000Z","msg":"多數會倒落廁所<br />\n如果多廚餘 驚沖唔到廁<br />\n會包多兩三個膠袋先放出走廊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T08:33:18.000Z","msg":"放出走廊?"},{"pid":"7d039a70e1552db99587e1913f7fa8b37639f9ac","tid":2385794,"uid":103263,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"85d937b6c5b4f9c7d2f0c10fc7281dacfdc30e2d","tid":2385794,"uid":103263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"re